OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUnaffordable pay rises     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwould be short-sighted - PM
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Rishi Sunak has said any pay offer to  
OL,6, public sector workers had to be "fair, 
OL,7, affordable and responsible" in order to
OL,8, control rising prices.                 
OL,10,FThe PM said it would be "short-sighted"
OL,11,Fto do something now that made inflation
OL,12,Fworse in the longer term.              
OL,14,FTackling inflation meant taking        
OL,15,F"difficult decisions" that would       
OL,16,Fbenefit the country, he added.         
OL,18,FIt comes as he reportedly faces        
OL,19,Fpressure from ministers to accept the  
OL,20,Frecommendations of pay review bodies.  
